dataset.name: place
dataset.sql: ${ "select m.placedesc,o.state,count(1) as number from tb_place_order o inner join tb_place_manage m on o.placeid=m.id COLLATE Chinese_PRC_CI_AI_WS where 1=1" + ( emptyparam("starttime")==false && emptyparam("endtime")==false && param ("starttime") == param ("endtime") ? " and ordertime = \'" + replace(param("starttime"),"-","") + "\'" : "" ) + ( emptyparam("starttime")==false && emptyparam("endtime")==false && param ("starttime") != param ("endtime") ? " and ordertime >= \'" + replace(param("starttime"),"-","") + "\' and ordertime <= \'" + replace(param("endtime"),"-","") + "\' " : "" ) + ( emptyparam("starttime")==false && emptyparam("endtime")==true ? " and ordertime >= \'" + replace(param("starttime"),"-","") + "\' " : "") + ( emptyparam("starttime")==true && emptyparam("endtime")==false ? " and ordertime <= \'" + replace(param("endtime"),"-","") + "\' " : "")+ "GROUP BY m.placedesc,o.state" }
